      <title>南非延长临时签证申请优惠政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/south-africa-extends-temporary-visa-concession-for-applications</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新任南非内政部长莱昂·施赖伯 (Leon Schreiber) 将对目前正在等待签证、豁免和上诉申请结果的外国人的临时优惠期限延长至 12 月 31 日。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/south-africa-extends-temporary-visa-concession-for-applications</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 06:14:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
