      <title>菲律宾因六月海上冲突向中国索赔 100 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/philippines-demanding-1-million-from-china-over-june-sea-clash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾军方负责人罗密欧·布劳纳周四表示，菲律宾要求中国赔偿上个月在南海发生的冲突造成的 6000 万比索（100 万美元）的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/philippines-demanding-1-million-from-china-over-june-sea-clash</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 03:55:42 GMT</pubDate>
